#: instructor-training/_episodes/05-memory.md:154
msgid ""
"A quick count shows that there are actually 6 things here,\n"
"not just 3,\n"
"so we're already brushing up against the limits of short-term memory.\n"
"If we add two more facts to show things that are usually (but not always) true:"
msgstr ""
